  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add nutella and tomato sauce to the skillet. Stir until well combined.",
    "Fold in bell peppers and onions. Cook for about 5 minutes or until vegetables are tender.",
    "Pour beaten egg whites into the mixture and stir quickly until scrambled, creating small pasta-like strands.",
    "Season with low-sodium soy sauce and garlic. Add green onions for extra flavor.",
    "Serve hot as a snack with whole grain bread or crackers."
